      "description": "\ud83d\ude98 Solid value and ready to roll! This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it's mechanically functional and gets the job done, making it a great option for budget-savvy buyers. The paint shows some visible wear and minor blemishes consistent with its age and use, and the interior has seen better days but remains serviceable. There's some work to be done cosmetically, but if you're looking for reliable transportation at an honest price, this one deserves a look. Come see it for yourself!",
