      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "\ud83c\udf1f Mint Condition Gem \u2014 Move-In Ready! This stunning vehicle is in truly exceptional shape \u2014 inside and out. The exterior gleams with no visible scratches, dents, or blemishes, and the interior is spotless with minimal wear on all surfaces. Everything works exactly as it should, and it drives beautifully. If you're looking for a vehicle that feels as close to brand new as the used market gets, this is the one. Don't miss your chance to own a genuinely outstanding car!",
