    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in good condition \u2014 a well-maintained used car that has been taken care of and shows it. The exterior presents nicely with only minor surface wear consistent with normal use; no significant dents, and the paint retains good color and shine with just a few small blemishes if you look closely. The interior is clean and comfortable, with upholstery and trim that show light use but remain in solid shape. Mechanically, the car has been reliably maintained and drives confidently, making it a dependable choice for everyday use. This is a honest, solid used car that delivers real value \u2014 not perfect, but genuinely good and ready to serve its next owner well.",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in mint condition, and we're thrilled to present one of the finest examples you'll find on the market. The exterior is virtually flawless \u2014 the paint retains its deep, original luster with no fading, scratches, or blemishes to speak of. Body panels are perfectly aligned, all trim pieces are intact and pristine, and the glass is crystal clear throughout. Step inside and you'll find an interior that looks and smells showroom-fresh \u2014 the upholstery shows no wear, the dashboard and door panels are spotless, and every surface is in exceptional shape. Mechanically, this car performs exactly as it should \u2014 the engine starts immediately, runs smoothly and quietly, and all systems function perfectly. Tires have substantial tread remaining, brakes are responsive, and there are no warning lights or known issues of any kind. Service history is clean and up to date. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been meticulously cared for from day one \u2014 if you're looking for the best, this is it.",
      "price": 47000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to purchase a vehicle in truly mint condition \u2014 and we mean that sincerely. The exterior is flawless: the paint is deep, glossy, and free of any scratches, chips, swirl marks, or fading. Every panel aligns perfectly, and the trim and chrome accents are pristine. The interior is equally impressive \u2014 the upholstery shows no wear, staining, or cracking, the carpets are spotless, and every surface looks and feels as though it just rolled off the showroom floor. All electronics, controls, and features function exactly as intended, with zero glitches or quirks. Under the hood, the engine is clean, well-maintained, and runs with the smooth, confident power you'd expect from a vehicle treated with exceptional care throughout its life. The tires have excellent tread remaining and wear evenly, and the brakes are in top condition. There are no known mechanical issues, no deferred maintenance, and no hidden surprises. A pre-purchase inspection is warmly welcomed \u2014 we're confident this car will impress even the most discerning buyer. If you're looking for a vehicle you can drive with pride from day one, this is it.",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
